Title: coolercontrol-liqctld no longer a separate package
Author: Alfred Wingate <parona@protonmail.com>
Posted: 2025-10-07
Revision: 1
News-Item-Format: 2.0
Display-If-Installed: sys-apps/coolercontrol-liqctld

sys-apps/coolercontrol-liqctld is no longer a separate package in 3.0.0[1].
It has been integrated into sys-apps/coolercontrold and you can enable
support for it with the liqctld use flag.

[1] https://gitlab.com/coolercontrol/coolercontrol/-/releases/3.0.0#removed
